Harmony Restarts Operations at Tshepong Mine After July 12 Death of Worker

-- B y   M k h u l u l i   M a n c o t y w a
-- 
2011-07-19T07:37:26Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-19/harmony-restarts-operations-at-tshepong-mine-after-july-12-death-of-worker.html
Harmony Gold Mining Co. said it
restarted operations at its Tshepong mine in  South Africa  after
the death of worker in an accident on July 12. Harmony Gold
spokeswoman Henrika Basterfield commented in an e-mailed
response to questions today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Mkhululi Mancotywa in Johannesburg at 
